            <span class="text-sm text-gray-300 group-hover:text-indigo-300 transition-colors">Endgame Strategy — master the final 10 tiles once the bag empties</span>
          </a>
          <a href="/blog/rack-management-basics/" class="flex items-center gap-2 p-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-indigo-900/20 transition-all group">
